creator: AIA Myanmar
descriptionHtml:
AIA MyanX app is a mobile application for AIA Myanmar members to access their member card and get access to AIA member-exclusive benefits from the extensive partner list. help you on your journey of healthier, longer and better lives. In addition, AIA members can claim their insurance policy benefits with ease, with an end-to-end digital process, a three-step claim submission process, ability to track status of benefit claims, and more importantly a commitment to process claims within 72 hours.

Current features available on the AIA MyanX app includes:
• Access to AIA Myanmar Member card to help avail AIA’s exclusive partner propositions.
• List of all Healthcare and Education proposition partners, along with AIA exclusive benefit details
• Digital and end-to-end paperless process to claim benefits for all your policies
• Ability to track the status of benefit claims, against our settlement commitment of 72 hours!
Thanks for being a part of AIA family!

creator: AIA Myanmar
descriptionHtml:
AIA MyanX app is a mobile application for AIA Myanmar members to access their member card and get access to AIA member-exclusive benefits from the extensive partner list to helps you on your journey of healthier, longer and better lives. In addition, AIA members can claim their insurance policy benefits and manage their policies with ease, with an end-to-end digital process, a three-step claim submission process, and ability to track status of benefit claims and request policy changes.

Current features available on the AIA MyanX app includes:
• Access to AIA Myanmar Member card to help avail AIA’s exclusive member propositions.
• List of all Healthcare and Education proposition partners, along with AIA exclusive benefit details
• View detail policy information for all your AIA policies
• Digital and end-to-end paperless process to claim benefits and request policy servicing for all your policies
• Ability to track the status of benefit claims and servicing request with our commitment of 72 hours!
Download now! Let’s start your journey as AIA member!
